(952, 1, '2020-05-10 10:12:59', '2020-05-10 10:12:59', '<p>[vc_row equal_height=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1589194147241{background-color: #000000 !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1589194208536{background-image: url(http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/bg-side-11@2x.png?id=812) !important;}\"][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1589195140302{padding-top: 200px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"982\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"right\" css_animation=\"fadeInRight\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"2/4\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"bounceIn\" css=\".vc_custom_1589360363518{padding-top: 40px !important;}\"]</p>\n<p class=\"title\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 2.7rem;\">Home of Brands</p>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"983\" img_size=\"full\" css_animation=\"fadeInLeft\" css=\".vc_custom_1589360214950{padding-top: 70px !important;}\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1589194225420{padding-bottom: 100px !important;}\"][vc_single_image image=\"916\" img_size=\"medium\" css_animation=\"bounceInRight\" css=\".vc_custom_1589188639622{margin-top: 150px !important;padding-left: 20px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"bounceInRight\" css=\".vc_custom_1589360635309{padding-right: 70px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}\"]</p>\n<h2 class=\"header light aos-init aos-animate\" data-aos=\"fade-left\" data-aos-duration=\"800\" style=\"text-transform: none;font-size: 2.5rem;\">Exclusively represented premium international brands in Egypt</h2>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\"bounceInRight\" css=\".vc_custom_1589365618248{padding-right: 50px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;}\" el_class=\"sub-content\"]We are called the Home of Brands for a reason- for over a decade we have exclusively represented premium international brands in Egypt, covering a wide range of products and services.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1589107649683{background-color: #000000 !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"916\" img_size=\"medium\" css_animation=\"fadeInLeftBig\" css=\".vc_custom_1589195505001{padding-left: 37px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeInLeftBig\" css=\".vc_custom_1589195522753{padding-left: 60px !important;}\"]</p>\n<h2 class=\"header bold uppercase aos-init aos-animate\" data-aos=\"fade-right\" data-aos-duration=\"600\">OVER 40 YEARS EXPERIENCE</h2>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeInLeftBig\" css=\".vc_custom_1589365638578{padding-right: 30px !important;padding-left: 60px !important;}\" el_class=\"sub-content\"]Ezz Elarab was first started in 1975 with 1 showroom and 5 employees. Today, it is a leading Automotive Importer in Egypt with 40 locations and 800+ employees, representing 20 international brands and serving 15,000 + customers.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"816\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1589108883229{padding-top: 50px !important;background-color: #000000 !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_single_image image=\"982\" img_size=\"full\" css_animation=\"fadeInRightBig\" css=\".vc_custom_1589195585340{padding-left: 70px !important;}\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeIn\" css=\".vc_custom_1589195622035{padding-top: 50px !important;}\"]</p>\n<h3 class=\"title more-padding\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Ezz Elarab name is one of the most trusted and credible names in the Egyptian Automotive Industry.</h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][vc_single_image image=\"983\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"right\" css_animation=\"fadeInLeftBig\" css=\".vc_custom_1589195599624{padding-top: 80px !important;padding-right: 70px !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1589109383566{background-color: #000000 !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1589111096180{margin-right: 70px !important;margin-left: 70px !important;background-color: #090a0b !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1589111433264{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-right: 50px !important;padding-left: 70px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h3 class=\"aos-init aos-animate\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">OUR MISSION</h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeInUp\" el_class=\"sub-content-small\"]To consistently deliver a fully integrated premium automotive solution of excellent and refined quality of service.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1589111005863{background-image: url(http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/BG-2-2@2x.png?id=818) !important;}\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1589110027367{background-color: #000000 !important;}\"][vc_column css=\".vc_custom_1589111365748{padding-top: 0px !important;}\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1589111112762{margin-right: 70px !important;margin-left: 70px !important;background-color: #090a0b !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1589110966965{background-image: url(http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/BG-4@2x.png?id=814) !important;}\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1589111420212{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-right: 70px !important;padding-left: 70px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h3 class=\"aos-init aos-animate\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">OUR VISION</h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeInUp\" el_class=\"sub-content-small\"]To become the most trusted and renowned premium automotive group in Egypt.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_height=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1589112613345{padding-top: 100px !important;padding-right: 60px !important;padding-left: 60px !important;background-color: #000000 !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1589112525754{padding-right: 100px !important;}\"][vc_single_image image=\"820\" img_size=\"medium\" css_animation=\"fadeInLeft\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeInLeft\" css=\".vc_custom_1589195748771{padding-left: 40px !important;}\"]</p>\n<h2 class=\"header bold uppercase aos-init aos-animate\" data-aos=\"fade-right\">WE OFFER RETAIL SALES ACROSS ALL PRODUCT SEGMENTS</h2>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1589112656414{padding-top: 70px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeInRight\" el_class=\"sub-content\"]</p>\n<h3>If your looking to purchase a new vehicle, you’ve come to the right place- our dedicated sales team will find you the perfect car from our variety of brands, with unmatched service packages and prices.</h3>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1589195846900{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-right: 100px !important;padding-bottom: 100px !important;padding-left: 100px !important;background-color: #000000 !important;}\" el_id=\"counters-row\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][evc_counter digit_font_weight=\"900\" digit=\"40\" title=\"Locations\" title_color=\"#ffffff\" digit_color=\"#ffffff\" custom_class=\"text-center hard-grey\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][evc_counter digit_font_weight=\"900\" digit=\"800 +\" title=\"Employeees\" title_color=\"#ffffff\" digit_color=\"#ffffff\" custom_class=\"text-center thin-grey\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][evc_counter digit_font_weight=\"900\" digit=\"18\" title=\"International Brands\" title_color=\"#ffffff\" digit_color=\"#ffffff\" custom_class=\"text-center hard-grey\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][evc_counter digit_font_weight=\"900\" digit=\"15 K+\" title=\"Customers\" titl